16:04.338 --> 16:07.508
you'd be a hit.

16:07.550 --> 16:09.552
Well, now,

16:07.550 --> 16:09.552
there was a hit involved.

16:11.304 --> 16:14.307
Well, how can I say this? Um..

16:14.348 --> 16:17.727
Joey broke Stephanie's nose.

16:19.145 --> 16:21.397
You broke Stephanie's nose?

16:22.690 --> 16:25.192
You better go to your room.

16:28.488 --> 16:31.491
There is no way I'm going to

16:28.488 --> 16:31.491
school tomorrow for picture day.

16:31.532 --> 16:33.200
Last year I was sneezeburger.

16:33.242 --> 16:36.287
This year I'll be robo-nose.

16:36.329 --> 16:39.081
Steph, you know dad's not

16:36.329 --> 16:39.081
gonna let you miss school.

