True.

16:40.834 --> 16:44.128
Ah. But what if I don't ask him?

16:44.170 --> 16:45.839
Steph. Oh, honey.

16:45.880 --> 16:48.341
- Are you okay?

16:45.880 --> 16:48.341
- Yep, I'm fine.

16:48.382 --> 16:51.970
The doctor says I'll be

16:48.382 --> 16:51.970
as good as new in a week.

16:52.011 --> 16:54.013
Is there anything

16:52.011 --> 16:54.013
at all you need?

16:54.054 --> 16:57.642
Well, I've always wanted

16:54.054 --> 16:57.642
a big-screen TV.

16:59.143 --> 17:00.728
Go for it, Steph.

17:00.770 --> 17:02.856
