17:11.990 --> 17:13.407
[sighs]

17:13.449 --> 17:15.869
Michelle, what are you

17:13.449 --> 17:15.869
doing in here?

17:15.910 --> 17:18.496
What are you doing in here?

17:18.538 --> 17:21.081
Is this what you do every day

17:18.538 --> 17:21.081
when I leave for school?

17:21.123 --> 17:23.334
Sneak in here

17:21.123 --> 17:23.334
and play with my toys?

17:23.376 --> 17:25.127
Every day.

17:27.087 --> 17:29.173
Michelle, listen to me.

17:29.215 --> 17:31.718
I'm ditching school because

17:29.215 --> 17:31.718
I'm not taking my class picture

17:31.759 --> 17:33.720
with this thing on my nose.

17:33.761 --> 17:35.889
But you can't tell

17:33.761 --> 17:35.889
anyone I'm home.

17:35.930 --> 17:39.183
- Pinky swear?

17:35.930 --> 17:39.183
- Pinky swear.

17:40.142 --> 17:42.269
Okay, now.

17:42.311 --> 17:43.897
You have to do me a favor.

17:43.938 --> 17:47.483
Go downstairs to the kitchen

17:43.938 --> 17:47.483
and get me something to eat.

17:47.525 --> 17:50.277
And if anyone asks

17:47.525 --> 17:50.277
who the food is for

17:50.319 --> 17:53.072
you say, nobody.

17:53.113 --> 17:56.034
- Got it?

17:53.113 --> 17:56.034
- Got it, dude.

18:13.426 --> 18:14.552
