18:33.947 --> 18:36.198
This is not for me.

18:36.240 --> 18:38.868
- Well, then who is it for?

18:36.240 --> 18:38.868
- Nobody.

18:47.001 --> 18:49.378
Michelle, this sandwich

18:47.001 --> 18:49.378
