18:55.051 --> 18:57.428
- 'Michelle!'

18:55.051 --> 18:57.428
- Oh, no. It's Joey.

18:57.470 --> 18:59.430
Remember, I'm not here.

19:03.559 --> 19:06.312
Oh, Michelle. You are gonna make

19:03.559 --> 19:06.312
