19:06.353 --> 19:07.897
Too late.

19:10.900 --> 19:13.027
- 'Hey.'

19:10.900 --> 19:13.027
- Uh-oh.

19:16.072 --> 19:19.325
Hey, you, doggy.

19:16.072 --> 19:19.325
That's for nobody.

19:21.869 --> 19:23.329
