19:58.572 --> 20:00.282
Stephanie, what are you

19:58.572 --> 20:00.282
doing here?

20:00.324 --> 20:03.911
Joey says I never have to

20:00.324 --> 20:03.911
go to school again!

20:03.953 --> 20:05.371
Jess, look,

20:03.953 --> 20:05.371
she's way too embarrassed

20:05.412 --> 20:07.040
