20:05.412 --> 20:07.040
taken like this.

20:07.081 --> 20:09.709
We'll write her a little note,

20:07.081 --> 20:09.709
Danny will never know.

20:09.750 --> 20:11.085
Works for me.

20:12.962 --> 20:15.589
Now, Stephanie.

20:15.631 --> 20:18.801
Pal, you're only in

20:15.631 --> 20:18.801
