20:28.227 --> 20:30.771
I'm willing to take that chance.

20:30.813 --> 20:33.357
Let me put it another way.

20:30.813 --> 20:33.357
You're going to school.

20:33.399 --> 20:35.068
- But, Uncle--

20:33.399 --> 20:35.068
- I don't want any buts.

20:35.109 --> 20:36.485
Now, go downstairs

20:35.109 --> 20:36.485
